              <h2>Real trips, field-tested notes, and a rig that takes us there.</h2>
              <p class="lede">
                We explore nature, document the places we reach, and bring back stories, photos, and
                practical travel notes for people who love the outdoors, overlanding, and real
                adventure.
              </p>
              <p class="text-secondary">
                Every trip is planned around the honest questions a traveler actually asks — how do
                you get there, is it safe to park, what will the weather do, and what's worth
                carrying in. Our writing is the answer to those questions, shaped by the trail, not
                by a desk.
              </p>
              <p>
                <a class="card__cta" href="pages/about/"
                  >Read our story
